AID_G_Melee_Affliction_V2.name: Afflicting Strike
AID_G_Melee_Affliction_V2.description: +10% Weapon Damage. Causes Affliction damage for 6 seconds.

AID_G_Ranged_Affliction_V2.name: Afflicting Rounds
AID_G_Ranged_Affliction_V2.description: +10% Weapon Damage. Causes Affliction damage for 6 seconds.

AID_G_Weapon_OnHit_EnergyNova.name: Energy Nova
AID_G_Weapon_OnHit_EnergyNova.description: After 6 hits, trigger an explosion, dealing 106% weapon damage in a 0.5 tile radius.

AID_G_Weapon_OnReload_Explode.name: Paint the Field
AID_G_Weapon_OnReload_Explode.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon marks them as a target, stacking with each hit.  Upon reload each marked target explodes in a 0.5 tile radius dealing 65% of weapon damage dealt per mark applied and removes all marks from the target.

AID_G_Weapon_OnFire_DamageStack.name: Ramping Damage
AID_G_Weapon_OnFire_DamageStack.description: Every 10th round fired increases weapon damage by 15%, stacking up to 4 times.  Reloading removes the effect.

AID_G_Weapon_OnReload_DamageBuff.name: Active Reload
AID_G_Weapon_OnReload_DamageBuff.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon grants a 1.7% weapon damage and 1% reload speed increase for 2 seconds, stacking up to 25 times.

AID_G_Weapon_OnReload_DamageStack.name: Super Shot
AID_G_Weapon_OnReload_DamageStack.description: Each bullet reloaded grants a 16% damage bonus, stacking up to 5 times.  The first bullet to hit an enemy after reloading deals all of the extra damage.

AID_G_Weapon_OnKill_Spawn_HealthPickUps_.name: Gumdrops!
AID_G_Weapon_OnKill_Spawn_HealthPickUps_.description: Eliminating enemies with this weapon can spawn healing gumdrop pick ups.

AID_G_OnCrit_Cold_Snare.name: On Critical Hit Cold Snare
AID_G_OnCrit_Cold_Snare.description: Critical hits snare the target and nearby enemies by 30% for 4 seconds. Can only occur every 5 seconds.

AID_G_Melee_ExplodeOnCrit_V2.name: Spam Hammer
AID_G_Melee_ExplodeOnCrit_V2.description: Critical hits cause an explosion, damaging enemies within 0.5 tiles for 20% weapon damage.

AID_G_Melee_ExplodeOnCrit_V3.name: On Crit Explode
AID_G_Melee_ExplodeOnCrit_V3.description: Critical hits with this weapon cause an explosion, damaging enemies within 0.5 tiles for 43 base damage.

AID_G_OnCrit_ShieldRegen.description: On crit regain 2.64% of damage dealt as shields.

AID_G_OnCrit_SpawnEnergyProjectiles.name: Scatter Projectile
AID_G_OnCrit_SpawnEnergyProjectiles.description: Critical hits cause 7 exploding projectiles to scatter to the surrounding area. Can only occur every 3 seconds.

AID_G_OnMeleeCrit_PistolHeadshotDamage.description: On crit, increase pistol headshot damage by 40% for 15 seconds.

AID_G_Weapon_OnDmg_AfflictedEnemy_Knockb.name: Combustible Coating
AID_G_Weapon_OnDmg_AfflictedEnemy_Knockb.description: Hitting an afflicted target causes a small Knockback AOE around them (5s cooldown).

AID_G_Weapon_OnDmg_ApplySnare_V2.name: Entangling
AID_G_Weapon_OnDmg_ApplySnare_V2.description: Damage dealt with this weapon snares the target by 30% for 6 seconds.

AID_G_OnEquip_AnimalFriend.description: While this weapon is held, wildlife will not attack unless provoked.

AID_G_OnRangedFire_StackBuff_CritRate.description: Each shot fired grants +1.8 Critical Rating for 1 second. Stacks up to 15 times.

AID_G_OnRangedFire_StackBuff_Damage.description: Each shot fired grants +1.8% Damage for 1 second. Stacks up to 15 times.

AID_G_OnRangedFire_StackBuff_FireRate.description: Each shot fired grants +2.6% Fire Rate for 1 second. Stacks up to 15 times.

AID_G_OnRangedFire_StackBuff_Shield.description: Each shot fired grants +3.5% Shield for 5 seconds. Stacks up to 10 times.

AID_G_Ranged_HeadShot_BuffSwordCritRatin.name: Headshots Buff Sword Crit Chance
AID_G_Ranged_HeadShot_BuffSwordCritRatin.description: Headshot eliminations boost critical hit chance with sword attacks for 15 seconds.

AID_G_Ranged_HeadShot_ExplodeOnDeath_V2.name: Head Splitter
AID_G_Ranged_HeadShot_ExplodeOnDeath_V2.description: Headshot eliminations cause an explosion, damaging enemies within 0.5 tiles for 30% weapon damage.

AID_G_OnHeadshot_SpawnSparkBurst_R.name: Headshot Spark Burst
AID_G_OnHeadshot_SpawnSparkBurst_R.description: After 5 Headshots with this weapon, reduce your current health by 12.5% and deal 30-133 base damage based on the percentage of your missing health in a 0.75 tile radius. Can only occur every 6 seconds.

AID_G_Weapon_HitStreak_AOE_Dmg_V2.name: Combo Explosion
AID_G_Weapon_HitStreak_AOE_Dmg_V2.description: Landing 5 hits in a row on a single target causes a small explosion damaging enemies within 0.5 tiles of the target for 70% damage.

AID_G_OnMeleeHitStreak_Dance.name: Hitstreak Dance
AID_G_OnMeleeHitStreak_Dance.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon 3 times causes it and nearby enemies to dance for a short duration. Does not affect enemies that have recently been dancing. Dance does not affect Mist Monsters or Bosses.

AID_G_OnRangedHitStreak_Dance.name: Hitstreak Dance
AID_G_OnRangedHitStreak_Dance.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon 6 times causes it and nearby enemies to dance for a short duration. Does not affect enemies that have recently been dancing. Dance does not affect Mist Monsters or Bosses.

AID_G_OnRangedHitStreak_DanceAfflict.name: Hitstreak Dance n' Burn
AID_G_OnRangedHitStreak_DanceAfflict.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon has a small chance to cause it and nearby enemies to dance and take fire affliction damage for a short duration. Does not affect enemies that have recently been dancing. Dance does not affect Mist Monsters or Bosses.

AID_G_Melee_OnDamageDealt_IncreaseDamage.name: Broad Stokes
AID_G_Melee_OnDamageDealt_IncreaseDamage.description: Hitting multiple enemies in a single swing increases damage.

AID_G_Weapon_Melee_OnDmgReceived_DmgBuff.name: Damage Conduit
AID_G_Weapon_Melee_OnDmgReceived_DmgBuff.description: 5 attacks from enemies give you a 20% melee damage increase on your next attack.

AID_G_OnHitStreak_Freeze.name: On Hit Streak Freeze
AID_G_OnHitStreak_Freeze.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon 7 times causes them to freeze for a short duration. Does not affect enemies that have recently been frozen or Bosses.  Can only occur every 2.5 seconds.

AID_G_OnHitStreak_SpawnSparkBurst_M.name: Melee Hit Streak Break Spark Burst
AID_G_OnHitStreak_SpawnSparkBurst_M.description: Hitting an enemy 4 times with this weapon reduces your current health by 8% and deals 26-151 base damage based on the percentage of your missing health in a 0.5 tile radius. Can only occur every 4 seconds.

AID_G_OnHit_ChargeStormKingHammer.description: Hitting an enemy empowers Meteor Slam to summon meteors that each deal 313% of weapon damage in a 0.5 tile radius. Stacks up to 7 times, summoning 1 meteor per stack. All stacks are removed on using Meteor Slam or switching weapons.

AID_G_OnHit_ChargeStormKingSword.description: Hitting an enemy empowers Storm Wave to shoot a piercing wave of energy, dealing 245% of weapon damage. Stacks up to 7 times, increasing the width of the wave with each stack. All stacks are removed on using Storm Wave or switching weapons.

AID_G_MeleeDmgVsFire.name: Melee Damage vs Fire
AID_G_MeleeDmgVsFire.description: Weapon hits deal 44% bonus damage against fire elemental enemies.

AID_G_MeleeDmgVsIce.name: Melee Damage vs Ice
AID_G_MeleeDmgVsIce.description: Weapon hits deal 44% bonus damage against water elemental enemies.

AID_G_MeleeDmgVsLightning.name: Melee Damage vs Lightning
AID_G_MeleeDmgVsLightning.description: Weapon hits deal 44% bonus damage against nature elemental enemies.

AID_G_RangedDmgVsFire.name: Ranged Damage vs Fire
AID_G_RangedDmgVsFire.description: Weapon hits deal 44% bonus damage against fire elemental enemies.

AID_G_RangedDmgVsIce.name: Ranged Damage vs Ice
AID_G_RangedDmgVsIce.description: Weapon hits deal 44% bonus damage against water elemental enemies.

AID_G_RangedDmgVsLightning.name: Ranged Damage vs Lightning
AID_G_RangedDmgVsLightning.description: Weapon hits deal 44% bonus damage against nature elemental enemies.

AID_G_OnHit_Execute.description: Damage dealt to enemies below 15% health will immediately eliminate them. Does not affect Mist Monsters or Bosses.

AID_G_OnHit_ApplyHuntersMark.name: Hunters Mark
AID_G_OnHit_ApplyHuntersMark.description: Keeping the bow drawn past max charge will fire an arrow that debuffs the target, increasing their damage taken from all sources by 20% for 10 seconds. Does not affect Bosses.

AID_G_OnHit_Stun_Lovestruck.name: Lovestruck
AID_G_OnHit_Stun_Lovestruck.description: Keeping the bow drawn past max charge will fire an arrow that stuns the enemy for 10 seconds. Weapon damage will break this effect. Does not affect Bosses or enemies that have recently been Lovestruck.

AID_G_OnHit_ShieldRegen.description: On hitting an enemy with this weapon regain 5.5% of damage dealt as shields.

AID_G_OnHit_ShieldRegenAndMaxShield.description: If this weapon hits an enemy, your shield is replenished for 3% of the damage dealt and you gain 20% max shields for 8 seconds

AID_G_OnHit_SlowToFreeze.name: Slow To Freeze
AID_G_OnHit_SlowToFreeze.description: Each hit applies a stack of slow. When an enemy reaches 10 stacks, they are frozen for 3 seconds

AID_G_OnHit_SpreadFire.description: Hitting an enemy spreads fire affliction to up to 6 nearby enemies in a 1 tile radius.

AID_G_OnMeleeHit_StackBuff_Armor.name: Armored Strike
AID_G_OnMeleeHit_StackBuff_Armor.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon grants +8 Armor for 5 seconds. Stacks up to 5 times.

AID_G_OnMeleeHit_StackBuff_CritRate.name: Critical Frenzy
AID_G_OnMeleeHit_StackBuff_CritRate.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon grants +6 Critical Rating for 5 seconds. Stacks up to 5 times.

AID_G_OnMeleeHit_StackBuff_Damage.name: Heavy Blows
AID_G_OnMeleeHit_StackBuff_Damage.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon grants +6% Damage for 5 seconds. Stacks up to 5 times.

AID_G_OnMeleeHit_StackBuff_FireRate.name: Frenzy
AID_G_OnMeleeHit_StackBuff_FireRate.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon grants +6% Attack Speed for 5 seconds. Stacks up to 5 times.

AID_G_OnMeleeHit_StackBuff_MoveSpeed.name: Swiftness
AID_G_OnMeleeHit_StackBuff_MoveSpeed.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon grants +6% Movement Speed for 5 seconds. Stacks up to 5 times.

AID_G_OnMeleeHit_Stack_AOE_Stun.description: Every 8th hit cause a stun around the character.

AID_G_OnHit_Stack_StormkingAssault.description: Hitting an enemy applies a charge. Building up to 5 charges or switching targets detonates the charges, dealing 100% of weapon damage to the target and nearby enemies. Each charge increases the radius, up to a max of 0.75 tiles.

AID_G_OnImpactBreak_DealDamage.name: Impact Break Deal Damage
AID_G_OnImpactBreak_DealDamage.description: Stunning or Knocking back an enemy deals them 12 base damage.

AID_G_OnImpactBreak_Dance.name: Impact Break Dance
AID_G_OnImpactBreak_Dance.description: Stunning or Knocking back an enemy with this weapon causes it and nearby enemies to dance for a short duration. Does not affect enemies that have recently been dancing. Dance does not affect Mist Monsters or Bosses.

AID_G_OnImpactBreak_Freeze.name: Impact Break Freeze
AID_G_OnImpactBreak_Freeze.description: Stunning or knocking back an enemy with this weapon causes nearby enemies to freeze for a short duration. Does not affect enemies that have recently been frozen, Mist Monsters, or Bosses. Can only occur every 1 second.

AID_G_OnImpact_SpawnSparkBurst_M.name: Melee Impact Break Spark Burst
AID_G_OnImpact_SpawnSparkBurst_M.description: Stunning or Knocking back an enemy reduces your current health by 8% and deals 26-149 base damage based on the percentage of your missing health in a 0.5 tile radius. Can only occur every 5 seconds.

AID_G_OnImpact_SpawnSparkBurst_R.name: Ranged  Impact Break Spark Burst
AID_G_OnImpact_SpawnSparkBurst_R.description: Stunning or Knocking back an enemy reduces your current health by 12.5% and deals 29-127 base damage based on the percentage of your missing health in a 0.75 tile radius. Can only occur every 6 seconds.

AID_G_TwoKillStreak_FirePool_V2.name: 1, 2, Fire!
AID_G_TwoKillStreak_FirePool_V2.description: If two enemies are eliminated within 5 seconds of each other a pool of fire spawns on the ground.

AID_G_OnKillStreak_Frenzy.description: Eliminating 5 enemies in 4 seconds activates Frenzy, giving the player and their tamed pet 25% bonus move speed and attack speed for 5 seconds.

AID_G_OnKill_ChainLightning.description: Hitting an enemy with this weapon causes chain lightning to strike up to 6 enemies. Requires the bow to be drawn back at least halfway.

AID_G_OnKill_ChainLightning_Real.description: Eliminating an enemy with this weapon causes chain lightning to strike up to 6 enemies.

AID_G_OnKill_Dance.name: Elimination Dance
AID_G_OnKill_Dance.description: Eliminating an enemy with this weapon causes nearby enemies to dance for a short duration. Does not affect enemies that have recently been dancing. Dance does not affect Mist Monsters or Bosses.

AID_G_OnKill_Frenzy.description: Eliminating a Mist Monster activates Frenzy, giving the player and their tamed pet 25% bonus move speed and attack speed for 12 seconds.

AID_G_OnKill_SpawnSparkBurst.name: Melee On Kill Spark Burst
AID_G_OnKill_SpawnSparkBurst.description: Eliminating an enemy with this weapon reduces your current health by 8% and deals 26-151 base damage based on the percentage of your missing health in a 0.5 tile radius. Can only occur every 3 seconds.

AID_G_OnKill_SpawnSparkBurst_R_Bow.name: Ranged 3-Elimination Streak Spark Burst
AID_G_OnKill_SpawnSparkBurst_R_Bow.description: Eliminating 2 enemies with this weapon reduces your current health by 12.5% and deals 29-129 base damage based on the percentage of your missing health in a 0.75 tile radius.

AID_G_OnKill_SpawnSparkBurst_R.name: Ranged 3-Elimination Streak Spark Burst
AID_G_OnKill_SpawnSparkBurst_R.description: Eliminating 3 enemies with this weapon reduces your current health by 12.5% and deals 29-129 base damage based on the percentage of your missing health in a 0.75 tile radius.

AID_G_OnMeleeKill_RegenShields.name: Shield Reaper
AID_G_OnMeleeKill_RegenShields.description: After eliminating 5 enemies with this weapon within 15 seconds, regenerate 25% of your shield over 3 seconds.

AID_G_Ranged_OnEnemyKilled_FasterReload_.name: Finesse
AID_G_Ranged_OnEnemyKilled_FasterReload_.description: +10% Reload Speed per enemy killed, up to a maximum of +50% Reload Speed

AID_G_Weapon_OnKill_Spawn_Firework_V2.name: Death Candle
AID_G_Weapon_OnKill_Spawn_Firework_V2.description: On kill: Spawn Roman Candle at enemy location (8s cooldown).

AID_G_Weapon_OnKill_Spawn_HealthPickUps.name: Candy!
AID_G_Weapon_OnKill_Spawn_HealthPickUps.description: Eliminating enemies with this weapon can spawn healing candy pick ups.

AID_G_OnKill_SpawnRetroSciFiRing.name: Retro Sci Fi Ring
AID_G_OnKill_SpawnRetroSciFiRing.description: Eliminating an enemy creates an expanding ring of damage. This can only occur every 4 seconds.

AID_G_OnKill_SpawnSteamCloud.name: Melee Steam Cloud
AID_G_OnKill_SpawnSteamCloud.description: Eliminating an enemy creates a damaging cloud of steam. This can only occur every 5 seconds.

AID_G_OnMeleeHitStreak_AoE_Freeze.name: On Melee Hit Streak AOE Freeze
AID_G_OnMeleeHitStreak_AoE_Freeze.description: Every 8th hit cause a Freeze around the character.

AID_G_OnReload_SpawnSparkBurst.name: Reload Spark Burst
AID_G_OnReload_SpawnSparkBurst.description: Reloading reduces your current health by 12.5%. On the next enemy hit, deal 29-132 base damage based on the percentage of your missing health in a 0.75 tile radius.

AID_G_OnTarget_CurseMark.description: Target up to 8 enemies while Aiming Down Sights to mark them with a Glyph. Releasing Aim Down Sights fires a salvo of projectiles that target each enemy marked with a Glyph.

AID_G_Shrapnel.name: Shrapnel
AID_G_Shrapnel.description: On hit, bullet splinters into shrapnel, dealing 40% damage in a cone behind target (1.5 second cooldown).

AID_G_StandStill_StackBuff_Damage.name: Bunker Down V1
AID_G_StandStill_StackBuff_Damage.description: Standing in place for 2 seconds grants +11% Damage. Stacks up to 5 times.  Moving from that position removes the effect completely.

AID_G_StandStill_StackBuff_DamageVsMist.name: Bunker Down Vs Mist
AID_G_StandStill_StackBuff_DamageVsMist.description: Standing in place for 2 seconds grants +17% Damage vs Mist Monsters. Stacks up to 5 times.  Moving from that position removes the effect completely.

AID_G_StandStill_StackBuff_GrantShield.name: Bunker Down Grant Shield
AID_G_StandStill_StackBuff_GrantShield.description: Standing in place for 1 second regenerates 10% of your max shield value.

AID_G_StormKingLauncherCharge.description: Charging this weapon causes the laser to split and chain to multiple targets on hitting. Longer charge times increase the number of splits, up to a max of 3. Charged shots generate more heat and consume more ammo.

AID_G_StormKingPistolHomingProjectiles.description: Fires homing projectiles that seek out the target's head. Aiming down sights increases the lock-on range from 4 tiles to 12, but decreases fire rate by 50%.

AID_G_Ranged_HeadShotStreak_DmgBonus_V2.name: Consecutive Headshot Bonus
AID_G_Ranged_HeadShotStreak_DmgBonus_V2.description: Getting 5 headshots in a row increases ranged weapon damage +30% for 10 seconds.

AID_G_Ranged_IsTargeting_DmgBuff_V2.name: Precision Scope
AID_G_Ranged_IsTargeting_DmgBuff_V2.description: +30% Weapon Damage when aiming down sights

AID_G_Weapon_OnShieldBreak_IncendiaryAOE.name: Burning Shield Break
AID_G_Weapon_OnShieldBreak_IncendiaryAOE.description: Deals Fire damage to nearby enemies when your shield breaks

AID_G_Weapon_OnDmgDealt_GiveEnergy_V2.name: Energizing
AID_G_Weapon_OnDmgDealt_GiveEnergy_V2.description: Damage dealt with this weapon recovers 5 energy. This can happen once every 4 seconds.

AID_G_Weapon_OnDmgDealt_GiveShield_V2.name: Shield Capacitor
AID_G_Weapon_OnDmgDealt_GiveShield_V2.description: Damage dealt with this weapon recovers 10% of maximum shield. This can happen once every 3 seconds.

AID_G_Woosh.name: Woosh
AID_G_Woosh.description: After 3 eliminations, gain +28% movement speed and +52% damage for 8 seconds.
